beer.beer_description:
What could be better than a taco? TWO tacos. It's almost impossible to only eat one taco, so we felt it was time to double down and deliver Double Taco!

This classic Two Birds brew has been amped up just for Beer Cartel, and now features more corn, coriander and lime than ever before. It might have been a party before, but now it's una gran fiesta!
